=Description=

"The book was pioneering for its time exploring the relationship between modern technology and society. It dissects the connection between social and economic conditions and the development of technique, showing how these forces interact. It asks Will computers be the agents of a new authoritarianism, more thorough and unassailable than anything yet known? Or will they open the way to human liberation"

